Package: spatzli
Version: 0.0.1
Title: Functions for analyzing spatial transcriptomics data
Description: Methods and visualizations for analyzing spatial transcriptomics data. Currently focused on data from the 10x Genomics Visium platform. Includes functions for preprocessing (quality control, filtering) and feature selection (spatially variable genes).
